@page "/about"

<PageTitle>About | Charmone Strauss</PageTitle>

<div class="about-page">

    <div class="about-hero">
        <div class="about-tag">ABOUT ME</div>
        <h1 class="about-title">Charmone<br />Strauss</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="about-content">

        <div class="about-block">
            <div class="about-label">WHO I AM</div>
            <p class="about-text">
                I am a 20-year-old Higher Certificate graduate from Greenside Design Center,
                currently pursuing my Bachelor's degree. A proud alumna of Hoërskool Driehoek
                (Class of 2024), I am deeply passionate about multimedia design and photography.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-divider"></div>

        <div class="about-block">
            <div class="about-label">MY STORY</div>
            <p class="about-text">
                My love for design started at home — helping my brother with his projects sparked
                something in me. From school assignments to personal projects, I discovered a
                natural ability to bring creative ideas to life. Design has always felt less like
                work and more like expression.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-divider"></div>

        <div class="about-block">
            <div class="about-label">WHAT I DO</div>
            <p class="about-text">
                In my free time I am constantly creating — whether it's small design projects,
                photography shoots, or exploring new creative ideas. Multimedia opens countless
                doors for me, and my ultimate goal is to break into game character and game design.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-divider"></div>

        <div class="about-block">
            <div class="about-label">EDUCATION</div>
            <p class="about-text">
                Higher Certificate — Greenside Design Center<br />
                Bachelor's Degree — In Progress<br />
                Hoërskool Driehoek — Class of 2024
            </p>
        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="about-cta">
        <a href="/portfolio" class="btn-primary">View My Work</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-outline">Get In Touch</a>
    </div>

</div>